data.description: Welcome to your new HOME!!! You don't want to miss out on this adorable ranch styled home. 3 beds, 2 baths, and a 2 car garage sitting on over a little more than a half of an acre. This charming home is located in a quiet Richlands neighborhood(Killis Hills) and has no HOA. The possibilities are endless! Also, don't forget about the short commute to Jacksonville, where the bases are located along with beaches, restaurants, stores, and much more. This home has updated landscaping, new ceiling fans, light fixtures inside and outside, paint, dishwasher, microwave, kitchen sink/faucet, LVP flooring in hall bath, and along with new sink faucets and new mirrors in both bathrooms. The seller is also very motivated and will help with closing costs. Come check it out!
